cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.RO, cs.SY, cs.DS 

The paper deals with Reinforcement Learning, which is a subfield of Machine Learning (cs.LG) and Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI). It also involves optimization and control of systems (cs.RO) and decision-making processes (cs.SY). The proposed methods involve data structures and algorithms for efficient computation (cs.DS).
